review:
Unlike the current generation of docs who misdiagnose issues. He is patient and administers step by step prognosis of the condition. And in time if the body doesn't heal, is when he advises surgery and other harsh alternative.
He explained the repercussions in terms of of short term and long term troubles/benefits. Also the anatomy of the knee was explained in detail.
